    "description": "Chapter 1 - is a free chapter of Enelia: Dawn of Madness. <br><br>If you'd like to continue your journey we're planning to release it episodically ou our Early Access page!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist Chapter 2 on Steam</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/7b8520c5cda43601e0ec2b0cbce58f7d.poster.avif?t=1720585051\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/7b8520c5cda43601e0ec2b0cbce58f7d.webm?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/7b8520c5cda43601e0ec2b0cbce58f7d.mp4?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enelia has dreamed of becoming a druid since childhood. In order to fulfill her dream she must defy the established Za'ani traditions. On the way to her goal, she learns a terrible secret that jeopardizes not only her own but also lives of her loved ones.<br><br><strong>Game features</strong><br>- Use Astral Vision to see what no one does.<br>- Make fateful choices and shape your own path.<br>- Build relationships with characters and creatures.<br>- Solve adventure style puzzles and mysteries.<br>- Collect lore in your diary.<br>- Reveal the truth about Madness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/f2bab5be4103d73e9c93403abfe3f318.poster.avif?t=1720585051\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/f2bab5be4103d73e9c93403abfe3f318.webm?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/f2bab5be4103d73e9c93403abfe3f318.mp4?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In search of salvation, Enelia ventures into an uncharted world with unique natural phenomenas, mythical creatures, ancient secrets, and members of a dark cult. You will embark on a dangerous and mysterious journeywith Enelia and her pet Shio in order to gain the power of a druid and find cure for a mythical disease called madness. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/ff71ddd82b90c0e3ecad27261a66290b.poster.avif?t=1720585051\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/ff71ddd82b90c0e3ecad27261a66290b.webm?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/ff71ddd82b90c0e3ecad27261a66290b.mp4?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>During the path you will explore wonderous landscapes, meet various characters, make fateful choices, reveal ancient sanctuaries, uncover world secrets and solve puzzles. <br><br>Our inspirations include Avatar, Princess Mononoke, LOTR, World of Warcraft, One Piece, Jujutsu Kaisen and many other!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/bc1e3edf5430be7f815eb6cdda69759c.poster.avif?t=1720585051\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/bc1e3edf5430be7f815eb6cdda69759c.webm?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041300/extras/bc1e3edf5430be7f815eb6cdda69759c.mp4?t=1720585051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
